<ab facs="#facs_92_r2l14">Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / dem <expan>ſelb<ex>n</ex>n</expan> ~ Stauffer vnd </ab>
