</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_92" id="44v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen Gebwolff vom
                            <expan>Degenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, vicztume czu Amberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vicztum, umb sölch sache und <expan>handlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>,
                        als der erber vest Dyetrich Stauffer und Sebolt
                            <expan>Pf<ex>inczing</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, von eins hofs <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        der von dem <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> reich czu
                            <expan>leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geet, miteinander
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb euch <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der römisch künig, seinen gewaltsbrief
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat und darümb ir auch
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Stauffer und
                            <expan>Sebolt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Pf<ex>inczing</ex></expan> vormals <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag
                        her <add>auf</add> den nehst <expan>vergang<ex>en</ex></expan> lantfride
                        bescheyden het, <add>darczu ir leiht kumen möht</add>. Also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>selbn</expan> Stauffer und auch
                        dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, einen andern <add>gelegen</add> tag
                        bescheiden und sie <expan>freuntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                                <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> richten wöllet, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
